text: Lisa Raymond and Samantha Stosur were the defending champions at the 2007 Sony Ericsson Open. They successfully defended their title by beating Cara Black and Liezel Huber 6-4, 3-6, [10-2] in the final. ==Seeds== # Lisa Raymond Samantha Stosur (Champions) # Cara Black Liezel Huber (Final) # Yan Zi Zheng Jie (Quarterfinals) # Květa Peschke Rennae Stubbs (Second Round) # Katarina Srebotnik Ai Sugiyama (First Round) # Virginia Ruano Pascual Paola Suárez (First Round) # Nathalie Dechy Vera Zvonareva (First Round) # Chan Yung-jan Chuang Chia-jung (Semifinals) ==Draw== ===Final=== ===Earlier rounds=== ====Top half==== ====Bottom half==== ==External links== *PDF Draw *Women's Doubles Draw Category:2007 Sony Ericsson Open Sony Ericsson Open
